asset.title: 2012, 2013 & 2014 Toyota Tacoma 4.0L Air Intake Installation
asset.description:
See how easy it is to add more performance to the 2012 or 2013 Toyota Tacoma 4.0L engine.

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=77-9037KP

K&N 77-9037KP air intake modification showed an estimated gain of 7.5 horsepower at 4976 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer.

K&N 77-9037KP fits the following: 
2014 TOYOTA TACOMA 4.0L V6 F/I - All 
2013 TOYOTA TACOMA 4.0L V6 F/I - All 
2012 TOYOTA TACOMA 4.0L V6 F/I - All 
 
Go to http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=77-9037KP for an up to date application list.

To search for your own vehicle's corresponding cold air intake and air filter visit
http://www.KNfilters.com
